            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Individual optimisations — title tag updates, content expansions — often show ranking changes within 1–4 weeks, as Google regularly recrawls and reindexes pages. Comprehensive rewrites of weak pages can move rankings within days for low-competition keywords.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
